These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, chestnut
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Color         | chestnut | amber |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, fonseca
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the person driving the tram##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Cigar          | bluemaster     | fonseca |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
City: rome, venice
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person traveling to rome is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| City    | venice     | rome |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini
House: palace, gothic-revival
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, pop
1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the fan of pop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Food          | zucchini   | strawberry  |
| House         | palace | gothic-revival     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | pop         |

